Generic Dataset / DataLoader¶

class ImageOnlyDataset[source]

ImageOnlyDataset(img_label_dataset, img_idx=0) :: Dataset

常用於生成任務，只回傳圖片而不回傳標籤的 Dataset

class ImageDataset[source]

ImageDataset(root, transform=None, image_exts=None, read='pil') :: Dataset

將指定路徑的圖片讀入並轉換成數據集。各個數據集的轉換由上游自行決定

用 PIL 或是 opencv2 讀圖都能得到相同結果：

transform = transforms.Compose([
    transforms.Resize((64, 64)),
    transforms.ToTensor(),
    transforms.Normalize(mean=[0.5] * 3, std=[0.5] * 3)
])

root = os.path.join(get_data_root(), "crypko/faces")

x_pil = ImageDataset(root, transform)[0]
x_cv2 = ImageDataset(root, transform, read='cv2')[0]
assert torch.all(torch.eq(x_pil, x_cv2))

各類型數據集的實現¶

貼圖¶

class StickerDataset[source]

StickerDataset(sticker_name=None, size=None) :: Dataset

An abstract class representing a :class:Dataset.

All datasets that represent a map from keys to data samples should subclass it. All subclasses should overwrite :meth:__getitem__, supporting fetching a data sample for a given key. Subclasses could also optionally overwrite :meth:__len__, which is expected to return the size of the dataset by many :class:~torch.utils.data.Sampler implementations and the default options of :class:~torch.utils.data.DataLoader.

.. note:: :class:~torch.utils.data.DataLoader by default constructs a index sampler that yields integral indices. To make it work with a map-style dataset with non-integral indices/keys, a custom sampler must be provided.

MNIST¶

mnist = get_dataset("mnist")
x = mnist[0]

assert mnist.input_shape == (1, 28, 28)  # CHW
assert len(mnist) == 60_000
assert len(x) == 2
mnist.input_shape

切割數據集、改變圖片大小並不回傳標籤¶

生成任務有時不需要使用標籤資訊。

size = (32, 32)
mnist_test = get_dataset("mnist", split="test", size=size, return_label=False)
x = mnist_test[0]

assert mnist_test.input_shape == (1, *size)
# assert len(mnist_test) == 10_000  # FIXME: weird, output = 5
assert len(x) == 1
mnist_test.input_shape
